data.description: This home has been gutted down to the studs and re-built with sheet rock and drywall.  As you step inside this three bedroom, two bathroom home, you’ll be welcomed by an open concept living area.  The kitchen has an island with plenty of cupboard space.  With the master bedroom separate from the other two rooms providing plenty of privacy.  This home features a Rinnai on demand hot water heater along with newer double pane windows. This home nestles on 1 acre with a four car garage with electricity. Great for projects. There is a storage unit in the back.
